
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>

<body>

    <!-- Top Nav Bar -->
    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>  
<!-- Top Nav Bar -->

        <!-- Main Content Section -->
        <main id="donating-rewards-section">
            <header>
                <h1>View Donating Rewards</h1>
            </header>
    
            <!-- Introduction Section -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <h2>Why Donate Blood?</h2>
                <p>Donating blood not only saves lives but also rewards you for your generous contributions. Here's how you can benefit from becoming a regular donor.</p>
            </section>
    
            <!-- Rewards Tiers -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <h2>Donation Rewards Program</h2>
                <div class="rewards-tier-container">
                    <div class="reward-tier">
                        <h3>Bronze Tier (1-3 Donations)</h3>
                        <p>Receive a thank you card and a free health check-up at the donation center.</p>
                        <i class="fas fa-medal"></i> <!-- Medal Icon -->
                    </div>
                    <div class="reward-tier">
                        <h3>Silver Tier (4-7 Donations)</h3>
                        <p>In addition to the benefits from the Bronze Tier, receive a blood donor T-shirt.</p>
                        <i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i> <!-- T-shirt Icon -->
                    </div>
                    <div class="reward-tier">
                        <h3>Gold Tier (8+ Donations)</h3>
                        <p>Exclusive access to our annual donor appreciation event and a personalized donor certificate.</p>
                        <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> <!-- Trophy Icon -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
    
            <!-- Special Promotions Section -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <h2>Special Promotions</h2>
                <p>From time to time, we offer special promotions where you can earn additional rewards, such as gift cards and vouchers for local businesses, based on donation drives or frequency of donations.</p>
            </section>
    
            <!-- Loyalty and Referral Programs -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <h2>Loyalty & Referral Programs</h2>
                <p>Refer a friend to donate and both of you will receive bonus rewards! Our loyalty program also allows you to accumulate points for every donation and redeem them for exclusive rewards.</p>
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i> <!-- Users Icon -->
            </section>
    
            <!-- Testimonial Section -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <h2>Donor Testimonials</h2>
                <div class="testimonial">
                    <p><strong>John Doe</strong>: "I have been donating blood for over two years, and the rewards program really makes me feel appreciated. The annual event is always a highlight!"</p>
                    <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <!-- Quote Icon -->
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial">
                    <p><strong>Jane Smith</strong>: "Not only do I feel great about helping others, but the free health check-ups and rewards are a wonderful bonus!"</p>
                    <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <!-- Quote Icon -->
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
   
     <!-- Footer -->
     <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %> 
       
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>


</body>
</html>